gui.staticpower.battery_block_charging_t: Can charge a single item at a time!
gui.staticpower.sprinkler_description: When attached to a pipe containing water, keeps farmland watered and increases the rate of plant growth! Other fluids may provide better results.
gui.staticpower.sprinkler_experience_des: When attached to a pipe containing experience, converts the experience to experience orbs!
gui.staticpower.redstone_control_enabled: Can be controlled by a redstone signal.
gui.staticpower.experience_hopper_descri: This hopper is specifically engineered to drain the raw volatile power of liquid experience from a living thing!
gui.staticpower.rusty_cauldron_descripti: The BRAND NEW Static Industries Cauldron! Made from entirely recyled materials, this marvel of engineering will serve as a solid foundation for all your future endeavours. Warranty does not cover damages resulting from excessive rust. You have your tetanus shot, right?
gui.staticpower.clean_cauldron_tooltip: An elegant bucket, for a more civilized age.
gui.staticpower.clean_cauldron_descripti: None of those NASTY recycled materials here. Every atom of this glorious, lustrous metalic shell is sourced from only the most abusive and vile silver mines, resulting in near double the efficiency! Rest easy knowing that 6 full grown men and 3 donkeys died to bring you this shiny metal bucket.

gui.staticpower.digistore_crafting_out_o: This crafting request cannot continue as this network is out of storage space!
gui.staticpower.digistore_wireless_termi: Wireless Terminal must be first bound to a crafting terminal!

gui.staticpower.redstone_cable_input_mod: This cable will read a redstone signal.
gui.staticpower.redstone_cable_output_mo: This cable will provide a redstone signal
gui.staticpower.redstone_cable_input_out: This cable will both provide and read a redstone signal (not recommended!)
gui.staticpower.extractor_tooltip: Extracts items from the attached inventory.
gui.staticpower.extractor_rate_format: Extracts items every %1$d ticks & fluid every tick.
gui.staticpower.filter_tooltip: Stop unwanted items from going into inventories! No more messy chests!
gui.staticpower.retriever_tooltip: Pulls items from any connected inventories. Why push when you can pull!
gui.staticpower.digistore_terminal_toolt: Take a look at your digistore network's contents. You see everything....EVERYTHING!
gui.staticpower.digistore_crafting_termi: Craft straight from your digistore network! Use it to craft a crafting table, I dare you, you luddite.
gui.staticpower.digistore_pattern_encode: Why craft when your soon-to-be robot overlords can do it for you? Teach them how to do it! Encode auto-crafting patterns.
gui.staticpower.digistore_light: All the rage among the streamers!
gui.staticpower.importer_tooltip: Imports items into the digistore network.
gui.staticpower.exporter_tooltip: Exports items from the digistore network to the attached inventory.
gui.staticpower.io_bus_tooltip: An importer and exporter all in one!
gui.staticpower.regulator_tooltip: Keeps an inventory always  topped up to a specified amount!
gui.staticpower.crafting_interface_toolt: Give it recipes, watch it go! Attach to any machines and the machines become part of the digistore network.
gui.staticpower.machine_set_team: Sets the team this machine belongs to.
